16\. Now they quote also (the following verse).: But those sons whom an
uninitiated man begets, the wise call Vrâtyas, who are excluded from the
Sâvitrî; (that is a rule which refers) in an equal manner to the three
(highest) castes.' <span id="fr_981"></span>[16](#fn_981.md)

